Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:37.89,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's get! Cherry pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:39.48,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}RAN-RAN Welcome party
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:41.09,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look up! Sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:41.76,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:44.16,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The presence... of asteroids!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:45.76,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As they confoundedly collide and melt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:47.54,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sing loudly! Like a Sirenger
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.54,0:18:48.70,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:53.15,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll be the one with the last laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:19:00.05,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because I'm wearing a sailor uniform {\fnaquafont\fs34.5}←{\rs}And that's that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:02.31,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though it's only Monday!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:05.80,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm feeling horrible. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:12.85,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The summer clothes are so much better! {\fnaquafont\fs34.5}←{\rs}Oh, so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:15.96,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's getting close to 3 picts. Yet, I'm still hesitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:20.00,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}{\be1}Try your best! Get your spirits up! My Darlin' darlin' PLEASE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.47,0:00:04.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A cultural festival, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.06,0:00:06.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it's that time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:07.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We have tests coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.50,0:00:10.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a pain how we have to do so much in second semester.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.92,0:00:12.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you have to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.94,0:00:15.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...heading into our last cultural festival of high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:19.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Opening ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.30,0:00:20.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:22.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Every year...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:23.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...during the Outou Festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:27.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...groups of people perform at the beginning of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.85,0:00:32.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just had a great idea!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.36,0:00:35.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.90,0:00:37.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Our class has decided...
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.24,0:00:39.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...to host a fortune telling house for the festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:41.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so please come up with your own method of fortune telling...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:44.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...before our next homeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.54,0:00:48.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You worked hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:49.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was touched!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:51.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.29,0:00:53.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking about doing a cheerleading routine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:54.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheerleading?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:57.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,For the opening ceremony we talked about this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.63,0:01:01.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be the best performance to pump up the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:04.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It does sound flashy and fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.51,0:01:05.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:07.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be the talk of the town!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.77,0:01:10.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,B-By "we" you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.15,0:01:12.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're part of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:14.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked the teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.48,0:01:20.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and was told that the plan must be\N properly developed, which requires members.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.39,0:01:25.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What about you, Yutaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.66,0:01:27.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:31.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be physically hard on Yu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.08,0:01:34.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:38.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I might try if it isn't any trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:39.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.51,0:01:41.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.80,0:01:43.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're very welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:45.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Will you be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.72,0:01:47.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll probably be hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.26,0:01:50.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I might just hold everyone back...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:53.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I'd like to give it a try this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:53.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:56.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka's willing to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:58.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you two say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:02.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:04.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if everyone's doing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:07.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I have wonderful friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.33,0:02:09.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortune telling, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:12.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But do you even know how to tell fortunes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.12,0:02:14.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:14.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh my...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:15.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:16.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it your idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:21.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can just wing it when it's for a cultural festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:22.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.65,0:02:25.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your class doing, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:26.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:28.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're being generic and going the haunted house route.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:31.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A classic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:34.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't come up with any other fun ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:37.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:38.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:39.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought it was very appropriate...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:40.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.40,0:02:42.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The real-life demon's angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:43.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Knew you would say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.32,0:02:45.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:47.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Patty-chan said she wanted to do cheerleading.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:50.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:53.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I might work hard at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:56.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always absent...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:03:01.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I never accomplished anything with other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:04.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm feeling better these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.51,0:03:06.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What I've been wanting to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:08.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and what Patty-chan wants to do right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...might be the same thing, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:15.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it'll be pretty rough...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.81,0:03:16.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:18.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough people...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:22.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so Patty-chan was wondering if you could participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:23.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at sports...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:29.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If people like you and Minami-chan are there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.72,0:03:31.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I might be able to hang in there to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:36.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell that you're really serious about\N this, and Patty's also asking me for help...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:41.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:42.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:43.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:44.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Patty, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:48.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard about your idea and was thinking it over...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:52.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for a quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:55.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm holding a certain ticket in my hand right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:56.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:03:58.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think the ticket is for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:04.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.65,0:04:06.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You loved the Jam, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:10.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to exchange a hot handshake with Haruhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:12.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Handshake session!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:14.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go! I wanna go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:16.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aya in the flesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:16.62,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Konata...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:18.79,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,...weren't you about to say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:21.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:25.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work hard to make some memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:28.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:30.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the age of cheerleading, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:32.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of reasoning is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:37.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Patty came up with the idea of doing a cheerleading\N routine during the cultural festival's opening ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:39.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds fitting enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:42.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why the two of you will also be dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:47.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any other people in your class who can dance, Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:49.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:51.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just go on ahead without our permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:54.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I probably can't do that stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:58.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But we probably won't get another chance like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a once-in-a-lifetime chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:04.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be doing it with people we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, it's a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:07.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more fun if we go crazy with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:08.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.28,0:05:13.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You might be right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:17.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so easily convinced...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:19.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to prepare for my class project.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:25.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to make some memories\N during our last cultural festival together...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:28.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You always bring up friendship out of nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:30.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obviously an act!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:35.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-chan's really pumped up about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:39.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But will she be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:42.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I told her she shouldn't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:47.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But she was really earnest about\N wanting to accomplish something with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:48.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:49.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:52.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She said that they don't have enough people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:55.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I got involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:05:59.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I was a little forceful about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:01.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't push people into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:03.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just ask someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:04.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:06.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:09.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:10.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:12.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:14.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:17.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My class can just replace me with someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:19.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you guys can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:22.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kagami sure is cute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:24.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Cheerleading, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:27.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not confident I'd do a good job...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:28.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:31.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not too sure about a lot of things right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Especially in terms of volume.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:37.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd feel a lot better if you joined us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:38.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:42.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.85,0:06:45.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can be of help...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:47.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Boin—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:48.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Miyuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:50.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Testing is over...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:54.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so we'll be focusing on preparations for the cultural festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:56.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but don't get too relaxed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:06:58.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:07:02.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They could cut down on testing when we have school events...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:03.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:05.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:07.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on with the cheerleading thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:07.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:09.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Before testing started...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:11.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"They approved the plan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:13.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...is what I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:14.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven't heard anything since.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:15.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:17.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How irresponsible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:19.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna have enough time to practice at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:19.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:21.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:23.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we'll go ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:27.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't worked out the choreography yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:28.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't worked out the choreography?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:29.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we supposed to do then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:33.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also taking time to pick a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:36.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not easy to find something on Hare Hare Yukai's level.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:37.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:42.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:43.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were having trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:46.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you should have asked other people for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This was your idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:50.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so you need to be responsible for scheduling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:53.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So many difficult Japanese words I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:55.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say that when\N you've done perfectly fine up until now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:58.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At least get some of the choreography done today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:01.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll work out the kinks as we practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:04.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask someone who's free if you can't figure something out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:08.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki and I can handle general\N scheduling and reserving a practice location!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:09.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:13.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:15.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You were pretty against this idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:17.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but like...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:19.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're the most passionate one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:21.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:23.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do, Miyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:26.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be using tarot cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.89,0:08:29.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you, Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:32.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't decided yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:33.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:36.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something even I could do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:38.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:41.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How about one that involves reading shapes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:51.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This shape...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:54.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...means that your love fortune is good...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:56.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...m-most likely!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:08:59.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You just made that up, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:00.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Ya think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:06.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:08.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You want us to learn this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:09.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:11.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not an issue of quality...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:12.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks fairly difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:14.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:18.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we just simplify the harder parts as we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:20.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:22.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we get through this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:24.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...a wonderful feeling of satisfaction awaits us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:25.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:29.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're out of tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:30.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make a trip to the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:34.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then grab magic markers while you're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:36.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And some exacto refills.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:37.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cardboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:38.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Playboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:38.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Glue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:41.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Something weird got mixed up in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:43.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And if we need to buy so much stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:45.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...stop playing around and go buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:49.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we calling the yakisoba?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:51.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A Fragrant Breath of Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:54.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this Fallen Drop of Sunlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:56.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okonomiyaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:57.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:59.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't tell what's what on this menu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:03.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese culture is so fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:06.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This project seems to be abusing stereotypes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:08.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:11.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:12.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:14.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A Zuka cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:16.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:17.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:18.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:22.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cafe where you can enjoy shows in the spirit of Zuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:24.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With girls in shiny dresses...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:26.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and beautiful girls in male clothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:28.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...serving as waitresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.81,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1152,670.5)}Two for one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:29.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Male clothing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:32.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:35.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-chan and Minami-chan are the leads!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:37.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In their dazzling, beautiful world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:39.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When was this decided...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:41.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also worried about the cheerleading...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:42.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but is this going to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:49.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:49.22,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're very good, Minami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.22,0:10:50.85,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Then let's try it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:51.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:52.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're perfectly in rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:52.60,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:54.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.41,0:10:57.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Would that be considered sadistic on the part of Miyuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.29,0:10:59.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...or masochistic on the part of Minami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you put it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:03.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takara-senpai's dynamic dance moves...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:06.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...are probably putting pressure on Minami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:09.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget that and practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:15.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The cheerleading costumes are complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:19.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:20.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:22.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it's a bit embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:26.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,These kinds of costumes make the people watching happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.59,0:11:27.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:31.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...this outfit was chosen by one of those who like to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:33.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The one you mentioned last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:35.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The dreadful, older Tamura brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:38.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can expect some great Zuka costumes, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:41.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:43.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are doing a cheerleading routine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:47.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I take pictures?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:50.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Within reasonable limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:52.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:53.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:55.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't done it successfully yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:56.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so we're pretty worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:59.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use my power to charge you up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:00.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.48,0:12:04.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your power...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:07.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...might charge us up so much we tire ourselves out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:09.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:11.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty rough considering how we have no time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A cultural festival, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:16.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What did we do for ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:18.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We had what you now call...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:19.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:21.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...a manga cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:23.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All the boys in our class...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:25.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...brought in their manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:27.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you guys were ahead of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:31.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It may seem normal to bring manga nowadays...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:34.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but back when we were in school, they were strict about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:36.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You could only do it during festivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:39.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, people bring it to school...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:41.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it's not really approved...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:44.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A fortune telling house, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.51,0:12:45.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let everyone know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:49.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...to give me a good fortune if I come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:51.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But that wouldn't be fortune telling...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:53.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:56.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it when you were in school?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:13:01.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think each class or club had their own project.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:03.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The projects were stuff like haunted houses...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.96,0:13:05.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and okonomiyaki vendors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:07.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty standard stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:10.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rather strange how...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:12.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it doesn't seem much has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:13.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:17.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...was a study of a cultural item such as Paulownia cabinets...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:19.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...ever used as a project?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:21.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:24.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That wouldn't be any fun at all, now would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.96,0:13:26.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:27.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:28.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:30.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:36.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we can pull off an exciting performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:37.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:39.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not complete yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:42.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so hang in there to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:43.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is when...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:46.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's a big help to have Hiiragi here to take command.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:47.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:50.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be the only one left out of the memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:52.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:53.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stare at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:56.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.26,0:13:57.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:00.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:01.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No trouble at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:07.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that today's a rehearsal...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:09.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and only students are allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:10.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:13.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We, the general public...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:15.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...can't get in until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:19.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you to check before coming here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:21.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:24.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Akira-chan would be here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:25.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:27.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste of train fare!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:27.46,0:14:28.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If we still had that money...
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.55,0:14:31.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...we could have had hamburger steak or something fancy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:32.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:35.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I really dig this feeling of incompleteness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:36.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:37.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're walking around in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This serves as advertising.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:44.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your costume's cute, Kona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:47.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta start from the appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:49.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll read lots of fortunes today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:53.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In five minutes and fifteen\N seconds, you will buy soft-serve ice cream...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:55.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In five minutes and twenty-eight\N seconds, you will drop it on your leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:58.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It seven minutes and six seconds, you will hit your head on a sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.59,0:14:57.83,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortune telling doesn't mean to predict the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:14:58.71,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Word for word?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:01.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:02.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:03.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...we're just as good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:05.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It took till the very last second...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:07.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but we're finally done!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:11.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:13.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You look wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:17.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really embarrassing to walk around in this costume...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.55,0:15:18.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:21.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but it's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:22.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.43,0:15:25.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira Kogami's about to go on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:26.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.04,0:15:27.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:30.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Akira Kogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:33.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work hard today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:35.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:36.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...Sakuraba.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:38.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's like a rehearsal...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:40.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so we'll just be running some check-ups...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:42.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Countin' on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:44.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:45.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You handle the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:46.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:49.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the cultural festival planning committee chair, Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:51.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:54.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm letting Shiraishi handle the rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:56.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so let him know if you need something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:57.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:15:58.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.43,0:16:04.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:08.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have gone to the demon council.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:10.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:12.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:13.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We were going through things...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:15.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and got a little too excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:22.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:24.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an appreciated guest...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:26.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so we'll treat you accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:29.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:31.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,After this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:35.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...we'll need a mic check for Cape of Thirty Years on Lucky Channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:38.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to say whatever you\N want after the song onstage tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:40.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll do a good job of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:41.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:44.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please head to the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Shiraishi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:47.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.71,0:16:48.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:52.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming to see Akira, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:55.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you have lots of fun today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:16:59.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She longs to be in the arms of her beloved...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:02.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Will such a day ever come?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:05.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As she drifts alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:06.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...guided by his words from that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:10.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll go anywhere in search of a trace...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:11.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:14.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira Kogami-san with...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:16.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cape of Thirty Years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:19.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Would you mi—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:20.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:21.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.30,0:17:22.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me sing my song!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:23.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you it was just a check!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:25.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:26.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I give a damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:28.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to kill you, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:28.94,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,So many difficult Japanese words I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:34.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everybody ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:36.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last run-through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:39.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I came up with this idea a little spontaneously...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:44.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the fact that I've been given a\N chance to do something with everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:45.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...makes me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:47.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of worrying about success or failure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:50.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I just think we should have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:28.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like, oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:33.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:33.62,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:35.33,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}You're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:37.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We were practicing our cheerleading routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:38.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:40.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So how's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.94,0:19:43.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't wait to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:44.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:45.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirsty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:47.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:50.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I can buy drinks for hardworking young people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:53.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:54.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:56.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:57.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a special case, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:19:59.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In return...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:01.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...be sure to make the first event at the festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:01.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...a real blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:11.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:15.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:19.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It kinda feels strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:21.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:22.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:24.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm also feeling a bit melancholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:28.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They say you have the most fun when preparing for a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:30.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.22,0:20:32.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:33.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:37.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We may never stay at school so late again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:41.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You feel a bit lonely when you look at it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:50.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-Tamura-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:51.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is really strained.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.78,0:20:52.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:53.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.83,0:20:55.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My stomach hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.06,0:20:55.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:57.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're frozen stiff, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:21:01.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look so calm yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:05.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Being nervous helps you concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:09.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm so nervous I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:10.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Test. Test.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:14.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we will now begin the Outou Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:16.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The first performance today...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:18.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...was submitted by a foreign student, Patricia-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:21.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A cheerleading routine performed by a group of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:23.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's begin...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:25.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:26.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cell phones should...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:26.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:27.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:33.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Running into trouble at the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.74,0:21:36.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That relaxed me so much I almost fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:37.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Great timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.14,0:21:40.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that guy so lame?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:42.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that trouble tends to follow people around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:45.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess this is appropriate for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:48.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How we can never be serious, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:49.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:51.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y'know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.34,0:21:51.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:52.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:54.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.95,0:21:55.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.72,0:21:58.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's try that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:21:59.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it! Sailor Uniform!
