Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.45,0:22:16.87,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Your whimsical nature is acting up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:20.62,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sad. Put an end to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.33,0:22:29.67,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably dreaming about her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.67,0:22:31.38,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,With a sigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.38,0:22:34.76,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,So long in my dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.76,0:22:36.14,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,She is an Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:38.22,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,(NO!) She is a Devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.81,0:22:41.48,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,As far as you're concerned...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.48,0:22:45.69,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,...she's a girl who set a sweet trap for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.40,0:22:51.57,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Your love is paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.57,0:22:54.37,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Repeating over and over but now it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.37,0:22:55.99,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.99,0:22:59.16,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Within my lips...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.16,0:23:02.58,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, just maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.58,0:23:05.71,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe love is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.71,0:23:11.17,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,...a boomerang we throw.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.17,0:23:14.76,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, just maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.76,0:23:17.85,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe love is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.85,0:23:23.56,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,...a boomerang we throw.
